"dhammā sambhavanti sammādiṭṭhipaccayā."
msgstr ""
"And that is how right view gives rise to these many skillful qualities—right "
"view, right thought, right speech, not contradicting the noble ones, "
"convincing others to accept true teachings, and not glorifying oneself or "
